  <brief_title>Outcomes After Esophagectomy With a Focus on Minimally Invasive Esophagectomy and Quality of Life</brief_title>
  <official_title>Outcomes After Esophagectomy With a Focus on Minimally Invasive Esophagectomy and Quality of Life</official_title>
